---
import Base from "~/layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base
  wide
  title="信用卡分期 / 消费贷 IRR 计算器"
  description="按月费率换算真实年化利率（IRR）。揭穿信用卡和消费贷分期的“月费率 0.6%”话术：名义年化 7.2% 实际可达 13% 以上。支持提前结清是否划算判断。"
>
  <h1 style="margin-bottom:4px;">信用卡分期 / 消费贷 IRR 计算器</h1>
  <p style="font-size:13px;margin:0 0 8px;">
    把银行的“月费率”换算成真实年化（IRR）。再判断当前已还若干期，提前结清是否划得来。
  </p>

  <div class="tabs" role="tablist">
    <button data-tab="irr" role="tab" aria-selected="true">分期 IRR</button>
    <button data-tab="payoff" role="tab" aria-selected="false">是否提前结清</button>
  </div>

  <input type="hidden" name="cc-tab" id="cc-tab-hidden" value="irr" />

  <!-- Tab 1: 分期 IRR -->
  <div class="split" id="cc-irr-pane" style="margin-top:8px;">
    <div class="col-input">
      <div class="card compact">
        <h3 style="margin-top:0;">分期参数</h3>
        <div class="form-grid">
          <label>分期本金（元）<input id="i-principal" type="number" min="100" step="100" value="100000" /></label>
          <label>月费率（%）<input id="i-fee" type="number" min="0" step="0.01" value="0.6" /></label>
          <label>分期数
            <select id="i-months">
              <option value="3">3 期</option>
              <option value="6">6 期</option>
              <option value="9">9 期</option>
              <option value="12" selected>12 期</option>
              <option value="18">18 期</option>
              <option value="24">24 期</option>
            </select>
          </label>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-text-soft);margin:8px 0 0;">
          月费率指银行账单上写的“分期手续费”，常见 0.45% – 0.75%。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-result">
      <div class="card compact highlight">
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-text-soft);">真实年化（IRR）</div>
        <div style="font-size:30px;font-weight:700;color:#c0392b;" id="i-irr">—</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-text-soft);margin-top:4px;" id="i-irr-note">—</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card compact">
        <div class="kv-grid">
          <div><div class="label">每期还款</div><div class="value" id="i-monthly">—</div></div>
          <div><div class="label">总手续费</div><div class="value" id="i-fee-total">—</div></div>
          <div><div class="label">名义年化（月费率×12）</div><div class="value" id="i-nominal">—</div></div>
          <div><div class="label">IRR / 名义</div><div class="value" id="i-multiple">—</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card compact">
        <h3 style="margin-top:0;">为什么 IRR 比名义年化高</h3>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--c-text-soft);margin:0;">
          每期都在还本金，但手续费始终按最初的全额本金算。后期实际占用的资金越来越少，
          却仍按原始本金收手续费，真实成本因此被推高。详见
          <a href="/guides/credit-card-irr-trap">月费率 0.6%≠ 年化 7.2%</a>。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tab 2: 提前结清 -->
  <div class="split" id="cc-payoff-pane" style="margin-top:8px;display:none;">
    <div class="col-input">
      <div class="card compact">
        <h3 style="margin-top:0;">分期与已还情况</h3>
        <div class="form-grid">
          <label>原本金（元）<input id="p-principal" type="number" min="100" step="100" value="100000" /></label>
          <label>月费率（%）<input id="p-fee" type="number" min="0" step="0.01" value="0.6" /></label>
          <label>总期数<input id="p-total" type="number" min="2" step="1" value="12" /></label>
          <label>已还期数<input id="p-paid" type="number" min="0" step="1" value="4" /></label>
          <label>提前结清违约金（%）<input id="p-penalty" type="number" min="0" max="5" step="0.1" value="1" /></label>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-text-soft);margin:8px 0 0;">
          多数银行收剩余本金的 0% – 3%；部分卡 6 个月以内提前结清需付 1 个月手续费。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-result">
      <div class="card compact highlight">
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-text-soft);">建议</div>
        <div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;" id="p-recommend">—</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-text-soft);margin-top:4px;" id="p-recommend-note">—</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card compact">
        <div class="kv-grid">
          <div><div class="label">剩余本金</div><div class="value" id="p-remain">—</div></div>
          <div><div class="label">剩余手续费（不还）</div><div class="value" id="p-fee-remain">—</div></div>
          <div><div class="label">违约金</div><div class="value" id="p-penalty-amt">—</div></div>
          <div><div class="label">净节省</div><div class="value" id="p-net">—</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card compact">
        <h3 style="margin-top:0;">说明</h3>
        <ul style="font-size:13px;color:var(--c-text-soft);margin:0;padding-left:18px;">
          <li>“净节省” = 剩余手续费 − 违约金。&gt; 0 倾向提前结清，&lt; 0 倾向继续还。</li>
          <li>已收手续费不退；本计算只比较“后续要付的钱”。</li>
          <li>若现金紧张，即便净节省为正也未必要立刻还，要看资金用途。</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size:13px;margin-top:12px;">
    继续看：<a href="/guides/credit-card-irr-trap">月费率 0.6% ≠ 年化 7.2%</a> ·
    <a href="/mortgage">房贷计算器</a> ·
    <a href="/guides/prepayment">提前还款指南</a>
  </p>

  <script>
    import { calcInstallmentIrr, calcEarlyPayoff } from "~/lib/credit-card-irr";
    import { fmtCny } from "~/lib/mortgage";

    const $ = <T extends HTMLElement>(id: string) => document.getElementById(id) as T;
    const cny = (n: number) => `¥${fmtCny(n)}`;
    const pct = (n: number) => `${n.toFixed(2)}%`;

    // Tab switch
    const tabs = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>(".tabs button[data-tab]");
    const tabHidden = $<HTMLInputElement>("cc-tab-hidden");
    const irrPane = $<HTMLDivElement>("cc-irr-pane");
    const payoffPane = $<HTMLDivElement>("cc-payoff-pane");
    tabs.forEach((t) =>
      t.addEventListener("click", () => {
        tabs.forEach((x) => x.setAttribute("aria-selected", "false"));
        t.setAttribute("aria-selected", "true");
        const which = t.dataset.tab ?? "irr";
        tabHidden.value = which;
        irrPane.style.display = which === "irr" ? "" : "none";
        payoffPane.style.display = which === "payoff" ? "" : "none";
        renderAll();
      }),
    );

    function renderIrr(): void {
      const principal = Number($<HTMLInputElement>("i-principal").value);
      const monthlyFeePct = Number($<HTMLInputElement>("i-fee").value);
      const months = Number($<HTMLSelectElement>("i-months").value);
      const r = calcInstallmentIrr({ principal, monthlyFeePct, months });
      if (r.monthlyPayment === 0) {
        $("i-irr").textContent = "—";
        $("i-irr-note").textContent = "请填写有效参数";
        $("i-monthly").textContent = "—";
        $("i-fee-total").textContent = "—";
        $("i-nominal").textContent = "—";
        $("i-multiple").textContent = "—";
        return;
      }
      $("i-irr").textContent = pct(r.irrAnnualPct);
      $("i-irr-note").textContent =
        `银行声称的“月费率 ${monthlyFeePct}%”实际相当于年化 ${pct(r.irrAnnualPct)}`;
      $("i-monthly").textContent = cny(r.monthlyPayment);
      $("i-fee-total").textContent = cny(r.totalFee);
      $("i-nominal").textContent = pct(r.nominalAprPct);
      $("i-multiple").textContent = `${r.irrMultiple.toFixed(2)} 倍`;
    }

    function renderPayoff(): void {
      const principal = Number($<HTMLInputElement>("p-principal").value);
      const monthlyFeePct = Number($<HTMLInputElement>("p-fee").value);
      const totalMonths = Number($<HTMLInputElement>("p-total").value);
      const paidMonths = Number($<HTMLInputElement>("p-paid").value);
      const earlyPayoffPenaltyPct = Number($<HTMLInputElement>("p-penalty").value);
      const recEl = $<HTMLDivElement>("p-recommend");
      const recNote = $<HTMLDivElement>("p-recommend-note");

      if (
        !Number.isFinite(principal) || principal <= 0 ||
        !Number.isFinite(totalMonths) || totalMonths <= 0 ||
        !Number.isFinite(paidMonths) || paidMonths < 0 ||
        paidMonths >= totalMonths
      ) {
        recEl.textContent = "—";
        recEl.style.color = "";
        recNote.textContent = "请填写有效参数（已还期数需小于总期数）";
        $("p-remain").textContent = "—";
        $("p-fee-remain").textContent = "—";
        $("p-penalty-amt").textContent = "—";
        $("p-net").textContent = "—";
        return;
      }

      const r = calcEarlyPayoff({ principal, monthlyFeePct, totalMonths, paidMonths, earlyPayoffPenaltyPct });
      $("p-remain").textContent = cny(r.remainingPrincipal);
      $("p-fee-remain").textContent = cny(r.remainingFee);
      $("p-penalty-amt").textContent = cny(r.payoffPenalty);
      $("p-net").textContent = (r.netSaving >= 0 ? "+" : "−") + cny(Math.abs(r.netSaving));

      if (r.recommendation === "early-payoff") {
        recEl.textContent = "建议提前结清";
        recEl.style.color = "#27ae60";
        recNote.textContent = `相比继续还，净节省 ${cny(Math.max(0, r.netSaving))}`;
      } else {
        recEl.textContent = "建议继续还";
        recEl.style.color = "#c0392b";
        const diff = Math.max(0, -r.netSaving);
        recNote.textContent = diff > 0
          ? `提前结清反而多花 ${cny(diff)}（违约金高于剩余手续费）`
          : "提前结清没有明显节省";
      }
    }

    function renderAll(): void {
      renderIrr();
      renderPayoff();
    }

    document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>(
      "#i-principal,#i-fee,#i-months,#p-principal,#p-fee,#p-total,#p-paid,#p-penalty"
    ).forEach((el) => {
      el.addEventListener("input", renderAll);
      el.addEventListener("change", renderAll);
    });
    renderAll();
  </script>

  <p style="margin-top:24px;padding:12px;background:#fafafa;border:1px solid var(--c-border);border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;color:var(--c-text-soft);">
    <strong>免责声明</strong>：本工具仅为公开公式（IRR / 二分求解）的演示与教学，不构成贷款、消费分期或信用卡使用建议。
    各银行账单口径、违约金规则与免息活动存在差异，最终金额以银行账单为准。
  </p>
</Base>
